item.title: Jogulamba Gadwal Collector Inaugurates Share Ali Premier League – Season 2.
item.description:
<![CDATA[Gadwal: District Collector B.M. Santosh emphasized the importance of excelling in cricket and striving for recognition at the state and national levels. He encouraged young athletes to develop their skills alongside academics and make the district proud with their performance.
On Sunday, the District Collector attended the inauguration of the Share Ali Premier League – Season 2 cricket tournament as the chief guest at the indoor stadium in the district headquarters. Addressing the gathe...]]>
